data.description: This Charming Stone Cottage is straight out of a fairy tale, From the custom Crab Orchard stone arch entrance to the side arch patio you will find character and charm all throughout this 1468 Square foot gem. This cottage offers 9 ft ceilings with 2 bedrooms and 1 bath and lots of storage. This beautiful home sits at the base of Windrock Mountain ,so a great location for ATV Riders. There is a full unfinished basement with a world of potential, it is already plumbed for another bathroom. Close to schools and city center. Must see to appreciate the charm. Buyer to verify square footage and lot size.
